propertyDetails.description: This extremely rare gem in the heart of Historic Avondale, a neighborhood full of  tree lined streets, local shops, restaurants, and parks all within walking distance, has hit the market!  Renovated top to bottom,  this estate spans almost 3/4 of an acre, with panoramic views of the St. John's River and downtown Jacksonville.  The upstairs features 6 guest suites and  a full guest house above the garage.  Each room is expansive and airy, yet intimate and inviting.  Natural light pours through each room and the expansive porch spans the entire length of the house allowing for all levels of entertaining.  The location of this home is spectacular.  Not only close to all the fun of Avondale, but also within 20-30 minutes of all major medical centers, the airport, and even the beaches!  You must come see this remarkable home for yourself; words and photos truly can't capture it's greatness.
